源网站https://wiki.winehq.org/Ubuntu

sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386
wget -nc https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/Release.key
sudo apt-key add Release.key
sudo apt-add-repository https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/
sudo apt-get update
Stable branch[稳定版]：sudo apt-get install --install-recommends winehq-stable
Development branch[测试版]：sudo apt-get install --install-recommends winehq-devel
